A '''Nova Scout''' was a [[Scout/Legends|scout]] who had been inducted into the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic's]] [[Bureau of Scouting and Exploration Services]]' [[Nova Core]]. [[Talek Var]] was the youngest inductee into the Nova Scout "Hall of Fame," and also the first to be inducted posthumously. [[Burt Jaxton]] was a retired Nova Scout,<ref name="GG8">''[[Galaxy Guide 8: Scouts]]''</ref> and [[Ecclesis von der Agar]] was a decorated but befuddled member.<ref name="G9">{{GamerCite|9|Endor and the Moddell Sector}}</ref>

